-- GM Volt, Nissan Leaf, Hyundai Sonata Named Car-of-the-Year Finalists
-- B y   C r a i g   T r u d e l l
-- 2010-12-16T17:57:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-16/gm-volt-nissan-leaf-hyundai-sonata-named-car-of-the-year-finalists.html
General Motors Co.’s Chevrolet Volt,
Nissan Motor Co.’s Leaf and Hyundai Motor Co.’s Sonata were
named finalists for the North American Car of the Year by the
Automotive Press Association today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
